on in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Robert de Redeware was born about 1243, in Northumberland, England, United Kingdom. She married Sir Robert de Redeware Earl of Netherwitton in 1270, in Fenwick, Northumberland, England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"about 1243–":"umbes 1243–Surnud","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","1271–Female":"1271–Surnud","1243–Female":"1243–Surnud","1243":"1243","1240":"1240","1271":"1271","about 1243":"umbes 1243","1270":"1270","Fenwick, Northumberland, England":"Fenwick, Northumberland, England","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1243–":"noin 1243–Kuollut","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","1271–Female":"1271–Kuollut","1243–Female":"1243–Kuollut","1243":"1243","1240":"1240","1271":"1271","about 1243":"noin 1243","1270":"1270","Fenwick, Northumberland, England":"Fenwick, Northumberland, England","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1243–":"environ 1243–Décédée","1240–Male":"1240–Décédé","1271–Female":"1271–Décédée","1243–Female":"1243–Décédée","1243":"1243","1240":"1240","1271":"1271","about 1243":"environ 1243","1270":"1270","Fenwick, Northumberland, England":"Fenwick, Northumberland, Angleterre","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Robert de Redeware est née environ 1243, à Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Sir Robert de Redeware Earl of Netherwitton en 1270, à Fenwick, Northumberland, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"about 1243–":"um 1243–Verstorben","1240–Male":"1240–Verstorben","1271–Female":"1271–Verstorben","1243–Female":"1243–Verstorben","1243":"1243","1240":"1240","1271":"1271","about 1243":"um 1243","1270":"1270","Fenwick, Northumberland, England":"Fenwick, Northumberland, England","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, England, United Kingdom",